    .row.well
      legend.text-center Why buy with us ?
      .row
        .span12.text-center
          
          .pointSpan
            h5 Increase profit margins
            small Get competitive prices for all products.
          
          .pointSpan
            h5 Compete with big companies
            small We group orders from small businesses like you and negotiate 
              | better prices from manufacturers / producers.
          
          .pointSpan
            h5 Direct from manufacturer / producer
            small We supply your raw materials directly from the the manufacturer / producer.
          
          .pointSpan
            h5 Online procurement platform
            small Now you can manage all your raw material procurement easily on our platform.
          
          .pointSpan
            h5 Loyalty programs
            small We have exciting loyalty programs, to empower you grow even faster.
